Class AgencyConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.transitime.configData.AgencyConfig

  • public class AgencyConfig
extends java.lang.Object
    Configuration data commonly used for an agency. By splitting out these commonly used parameters they can be accessed without needing to access CoreConfig which logs lots and lots of params and clutters things up.
